Package org.jnetpcap.packet.format

Class XmlFormatter

java.lang.Object
org.jnetpcap.packet.format.JFormatter
org.jnetpcap.packet.format.XmlFormatter
public class XmlFormatter extends JFormatter
This formatter products XML output for a packet. A packet content is output as XML sheet based on field objects read from each header within a packet.
Author:
Mark Bednarczyk, Sly Technologies, Inc.
